    "description": "<strong>【 In this world, &quot;only what you see&quot; is true. 】</strong><br><br>This game is a 2.5D platformer puzzle action game in which objects seen by the character materialize, and when you meditate and open your eyes again, the object you saw disappears.<br><br>Enjoy the thrill of advancing based on your memory, and the pleasure you get when that memory is correct.<br><br><br><strong>◆How to operate the game.</strong><br>In addition to the basic movement and jump controls, the viewpoint control and eye close/open controls allow the user to enjoy a new puzzle experience unlike any other.<br>The game also incorporates a number of action elements that even those who are not good at action puzzles can enjoy.<br><br><strong>◆Stages</strong><br>There are a total of 50 stages, so you can experience the fun of this game to your heart's content.<br><br><strong>◆Story</strong><br>The main character has been deceived by the Internet society and wandered into a mysterious world.<br>Please enjoy the story of the main character as he asks himself questions in this mysterious world and &quot;derives his own answers&quot;.<br>Is the world really only what you see...?<br><br><strong>◆The challenge element</strong><br>After completing all the stages, think of ways to clear the game and play while collecting &quot;hearts&quot; in each stage.<br><br><strong>◆Distribution guidelines</strong><br><br>Game distribution: OK for both individuals and corporations<br>Spoiling: OK<br>Monetization: OK",
